# Migration Guide: Mock API to Real Pay2S API

## Overview
Hướng dẫn chuyển đổi từ Mock API sang Real Pay2S API cho frontend team.

## Migration Checklist

### ✅ Pre-Migration
- [ ] Backup current frontend code
- [ ] Review existing mock API usage
- [ ] Set up Pay2S sandbox credentials
- [ ] Test backend Pay2S integration
- [ ] Update environment variables

### ✅ Migration Steps
- [ ] Update API endpoint URLs
- [ ] Update request/response data structures
- [ ] Implement real QR code handling
- [ ] Update status monitoring logic
- [ ] Add error handling for real API failures
- [ ] Update UI components

### ✅ Post-Migration
- [ ] Test end-to-end flow
- [ ] Verify payment processing
- [ ] Test error scenarios
- [ ] Update documentation
- [ ] Deploy to staging environment

## 1. API Endpoint Changes

### Before (Mock API)
```typescript
// Mock endpoints
POST /api/v1/topups/create-mock-qr
GET /api/v1/topups/:code/mock-status
POST /api/v1/topups/:code/mock-webhook
```

### After (Real Pay2S API)
```typescript
// Real endpoints
POST /api/v1/topups/create-with-pay2s
GET /api/v1/topups/:topupCode/status
GET /api/v1/collection-requests/code/:code
POST /webhooks/pay2s/ipn (backend only)
```

